(15, 11, '', '', '0":;"About Fillmore":;"We believe wine appreciation should be about what you truly enjoy rather than what you “should” be enjoying and our selection of wines is for those who appreciate the characters and qualities of New World varietals. We hope you not only enjoy exploring them but that you will also share in our delight of life’s everyday pleasures.\r\n\r\nBe your own purveyor of wine and enjoy the world around you.\r\n":;"1":;"About Sing (Founder)":;"There are moments in our life when we reach for a Lafite or Opus, yet the ones I enjoy the most are the impromptu, casual occasions spent alone or with friends enjoying a glass.\r\n\r\nAfter years of buying wine, I noticed the selection has become wider and choosing has become harder, yet you only need one bottle you like. This is what wine appreciation should be about.\r\n\r\nHaving lived in California for 20 years, I wanted to bring its unique attitude and lifestyle to my friends in China. I have personally chosen a select group of wines because I believe that it’s not about having the largest most lucrative selection but about leaving the most memorable impression.\r\n', 'en_us'),
